EmailTemplate.description: Use this email when closing the loop with customer (e.g. resolved ICD but VM)
EmailTemplate.name: Issue Resolution: ICD Close Loop Email Template
EmailTemplate.subject: SunPower Internet Communication Resolved - {!Case.Contact}
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Dear {!Case.Contact},
Im very happy to inform you that the internet communication issue has been resolved. This is to confirm that your SunPower Solar System is now consistently reporting energy production information to our database. We really appreciate that you took the time to troubleshoot with us!
Your ticket {!Case.CaseNumber} will be closed today and a survey will be sent to your email separately. We are always looking for ways to deliver real customer value and use customer feedback to improve the service we provide.
To ensure that you are always up to date on your energy production information, you may log on to the SunPower Portal on your desktop at www.monitor.us.sunpower.com.
For your convenience I have attached basic troubleshooting steps to help you address common issues in the future. If you need further assistance, feel free to respond to this email or contact Customer Support at 1-800-SUNPOWER. Our team of experts will be happy to assist you.
Thank you for choosing SunPower as your solar provider.
Regards,
{!Case.OwnerFirstName} SunPower Customer Support 1-800-SUNPOWER (1-800-786-7693) www.us.sunpower.com
